"{\"uid\": \"rte.ie-sport-hockey-2024-0103-1424661-back-to-back-olympics-would-be-marker-for-ireland\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"  Sean Dancer is hopeful that this generation of Irish women's hockey players can lay down a \\\"marker\\\" by qualifying for back-to-back Olympic Games.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 147, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2, \"end\": 6, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sean_Penn\", \"score\": 0.7678582264902138, \"rank\": 0.24499243393438525, \"text\": \"Sean\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sean_Penn\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sean_Penn\"}, {\"begin\": 49, \"end\": 54, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"score\": 0.999867208689234, \"rank\": 0.00012626366840544345, \"text\": \"Irish\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Ireland head coach will lead his squad into the final qualifying tournament for Paris 2024 in Valencia this month.\", \"from\": 149, \"to\": 267, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 153, \"end\": 160, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"score\": 0.9956027046129563, \"rank\": 0.003321043073699026, \"text\": \"Ireland\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\"}, {\"begin\": 233, \"end\": 243, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.584700967884498e-14, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 247, \"end\": 255, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Valencia_CF\", \"score\": 0.9999443913635189, \"rank\": 5.5599096590081854e-05, \"text\": \"Valencia\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Valencia_CF\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Valencia_CF\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Making a second Games in a row would extend a golden era for Irish women's hockey, having reached the delayed Tokyo 2020 Olympics which had followed the unforgettable run to the 2018 World Cup final.\", \"from\": 269, \"to\": 468, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 330, \"end\": 335, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"score\": 0.999867208689234, \"rank\": 0.00012626366840544345, \"text\": \"Irish\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And Dancer wants to see his squad continuing the momentum that has been built in this era.\", \"from\": 470, \"to\": 560, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"That would be a really true test of the character of the group for us to be able to qualify for two Olympics in a row,\\\" he told RT\\u00c9 Sport's Clare MacNamara.\", \"from\": 562, \"to\": 719, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 691, \"end\": 700, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/RT\\u00c9_Sport\", \"score\": 0.9999999789533833, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"RT\\u00c9 Sport\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/RT\\u00c9_Sport\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/RT\\u00c9_Sport\"}, {\"begin\": 703, \"end\": 708, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clare_GAA\", \"score\": 0.9997856261593537, \"rank\": 0.00021441980654921986, \"text\": \"Clare\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clare_GAA\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clare_GAA\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Obviously, Tokyo was the first time that they qualified and the World Cup result was an excellent result for the team, so that would just show the level that the team has got to and their right on the world stage to compete against the best teams in the world.\", \"from\": 721, \"to\": 982, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 733, \"end\": 738, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9970306859939979, \"rank\": 0.002975695539575855, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I think it would be a real marker for us as a group and marker for the team to get that Olympic qualification.\\\"\", \"from\": 984, \"to\": 1096, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The squad will head to Spain on Saturday before playing warm-up matches with Canada and France.\", \"from\": 1098, \"to\": 1193, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1121, \"end\": 1126, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9999972979774282, \"rank\": 2.7005466949964627e-06, \"text\": \"Spain\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1175, \"end\": 1181, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada_women's_national_soccer_team\", \"score\": 0.9257106073867685, \"rank\": 0.08010748241279989, \"text\": \"Canada\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada_women's_national_soccer_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada_women's_national_soccer_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1186, \"end\": 1192, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9978995634450323, \"rank\": 0.0021048517375673132, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They will then face a tough challenge in their opening pool match against Belgium on 13 January before taking on Ukraine and South Korea.\", \"from\": 1195, \"to\": 1332, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1269, \"end\": 1276, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belgium_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9021279088661353, \"rank\": 0.10839310793153868, \"text\": \"Belgium\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belgium_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belgium_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1308, \"end\": 1315, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukraine_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9996579246823224, \"rank\": 0.0003421923680044496, \"text\": \"Ukraine\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukraine_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukraine_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1320, \"end\": 1331, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Korea_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9980802413921128, \"rank\": 0.0019234030167387818, \"text\": \"South Korea\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Korea_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Korea_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The top two in the pool will reach the semi-finals, where two of Great Britain, Canada, Malaysia and hosts Spain await, but only the finalists and the third-place finisher will advance to the Olympics.\", \"from\": 1334, \"to\": 1535, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1399, \"end\": 1412, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_women's_national_field_hockey_team\", \"score\": 0.9824597533431023, \"rank\": 0.017853160414319964, \"text\": \"Great Britain\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_women's_national_field_hockey_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_women's_national_field_hockey_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1414, \"end\": 1420, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada_women's_national_soccer_team\", \"score\": 0.9257106073867685, \"rank\": 0.08010748241279989, \"text\": \"Canada\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada_women's_national_soccer_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada_women's_national_soccer_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1422, \"end\": 1430, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Malaysia_national_cricket_team\", \"score\": 0.8491781700401004, \"rank\": 0.1651859223399295, \"text\": \"Malaysia\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q12973014\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Malaysia_national_cricket_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Malaysia_national_cricket_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1441, \"end\": 1446, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9999972979774282, \"rank\": 2.7005466949964627e-06, \"text\": \"Spain\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We sit fifth-ranked in the tournament.\", \"from\": 1537, \"to\": 1576, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We are going there to get a medal and getting us a medal in the top three would qualify us for the Olympics, so it is part of the bigger picture of where we are performing in tournaments and getting to,\\\" said Dancer.\", \"from\": 1577, \"to\": 1793, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"So world rankings are important but certainly we are not holding ourselves to that.\", \"from\": 1795, \"to\": 1879, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It is a tough tournament.\", \"from\": 1881, \"to\": 1907, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The top two go through to qualify for the semi-finals and then you play a semi-final, one and two play the final and three and four battle it out and the winner goes to the Olympics.\", \"from\": 1908, \"to\": 2090, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It is going to be really tough but certainly the way we have been tracking and progressing, including the mindset of the group, is in a really good place.\\\"\", \"from\": 2092, \"to\": 2248, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Dancer has overseen an expansion of the playing pool although that has meant increased selection dilemmas, with his squad for the Olympic qualifiershaving to be whittled down to an 18with a fair share of experienced names.\", \"from\": 2250, \"to\": 2472, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Two years ago we had a group of 20.\", \"from\": 2474, \"to\": 2510, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Now we are up to a group of 30 and that's 30 people competing for the team and that's really healthy - hard headaches obviously for me as a coach to make final selections but that's certainly the place we want to be in,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 2511, \"to\": 2740, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am really happy with the balance.\", \"from\": 2742, \"to\": 2778, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"There are a couple of players coming back into the group and that's also healthy for competition.\", \"from\": 2779, \"to\": 2876, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We have good experience, we have nine out of the 18 that qualified the team for Tokyo in 2019 and the majority of the rest of the group was there for the World Cup qualifier in 2021 as well.\", \"from\": 2878, \"to\": 3069, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2959, \"end\": 2964, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9970306859939979, \"rank\": 0.002975695539575855, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"So from an experience point of view, we certainly developed and gained a lot of experience.\\\"\", \"from\": 3071, \"to\": 3164, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00a9 RT\\u00c9 2026.\", \"from\": 3166, \"to\": 3177, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"RT\\u00c9.ie is the website of Raidi\\u00f3 Teilif\\u00eds \\u00c9ireann, Ireland's National Public Service Media.\", \"from\": 3178, \"to\": 3268, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3203, \"end\": 3226, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raidi\\u00f3_Teilif\\u00eds_\\u00c9ireann\", \"score\": 0.9993664851268295, \"rank\": 0.0006339164685885233, \"text\": \"Raidi\\u00f3 Teilif\\u00eds \\u00c9ireann\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raidi\\u00f3_Teilif\\u00eds_\\u00c9ireann\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raidi\\u00f3_Teilif\\u00eds_\\u00c9ireann\"}, {\"begin\": 3228, \"end\": 3235, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"score\": 0.9956027046129563, \"rank\": 0.003321043073699026, \"text\": \"Ireland\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"RT\\u00c9 is not responsible for the content of external internet sites.\", \"from\": 3269, \"to\": 3335, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3269, \"end\": 3272, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raidi\\u00f3_Teilif\\u00eds_\\u00c9ireann\", \"score\": 0.9835396432123026, \"rank\": 0.013767790549921992, \"text\": \"RT\\u00c9\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raidi\\u00f3_Teilif\\u00eds_\\u00c9ireann\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raidi\\u00f3_Teilif\\u00eds_\\u00c9irea